:868652,"uid":217281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"549dfd71015f2d4c28f1df246d2556e228a530cf","tid":868652,"uid":165404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abe5e1a312aa6738a7529d97e9f7d5c120623d34","tid":868652,"uid":92376,"like":233,"dislike":43,"score":190,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-10-20 12:16am-10:16pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/P4GOPNs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FP4GOPNs.png&h=82a27fe8&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OlQADnD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOlQADnD.png&h=73e28921&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(11)沈卓盈vs杜小喬(16)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:35:47.000Z","msg":"右邊果個同一level<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"有無post係討論杜小喬可以追<br />\n完全唔明大餅面點樣做到娘娘"},{"pid":"212fcbd395e9169dba564c1c2da6793fcaaa8726","tid":868652,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa033bc895161936302bee8f210050c2aa11e8da","tid":868652,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9cdb269ef3ba0b8a09d87e22bd275ff1ae4898","tid":868652,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10